description         \
    Multi functional app to find duplicates, empty folders, similar images etc.

long_description    \
    ${name} is a simple, fast and free app to remove unnecessary files from \
    your computer. It can find duplicates, empty folders, big files, empty \
    files, temporary files, similar images, similar videos, similar music, \
    invalid symbolic links, broken files, and files with bad extensions.
   
